{"synckey":1719920996,"updated":[{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_14_591-646","createTime":1719920996,"chapterUid":14,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"只要一有空闲时间就反复进行“30秒内说出10个事物的名字”“不使用形容词的表达方式”和“实况转播”这3项练习。","range":"591-646"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_13_1408-1487","createTime":1719894536,"chapterUid":13,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"根据TPO（Time，时间；Place，地点；Occasion，场合）来确定训练项目。不要偷懒，要通过思考、说话和“实况转播”来减掉大脑中“松松软软的赘肉”。","range":"1408-1487"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_12_1685-1714","createTime":1719533592,"chapterUid":12,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"“从单词到句子”的诀窍就是自己“实况转播”遇见的种种情景。","range":"1685-1714"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_12_1192-1248","createTime":1719533576,"chapterUid":12,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"请你在观看运动比赛的时候关注一下广播员的实况转播。因为他们能够用十分得体的语言来描述眼前的场景。这对你大有裨益。","range":"1192-1248"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_2668-2741","createTime":1719266954,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"所谓“逻辑”便是“道理”。大家要通过整理思绪、分条列点、俯瞰全局、举例说明等方式，掌握深入思考的能力。为达成这一目标，我将会介绍一些“思考模型”。","range":"2668-2741"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_2475-2506","createTime":1719266875,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"要在浑浑噩噩、蹉跎度日的生活中导入培养“思考”能力的训练方法。","range":"2475-2506"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_2519-2566","createTime":1719266863,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"思考“为什么要这么做”，尝试赋予其某种意义、建立某种假说。努力在每一天的生活中增加思考的机会。","range":"2519-2566"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_1395-1453","createTime":1719266808,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"别焦虑，放心吧！在这个世界上这样的人大有人在。不，应该说大半的人都不懂得如何整理自己的思路并运用合适的语言表达出来。","range":"1395-1453"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_1264-1286","createTime":1719266794,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"最重要的便是拥有“把思想转化成语言”的能力。","range":"1264-1286"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_1082-1098","createTime":1719266777,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"如何梳理自己的想法并传达给别人。","range":"1082-1098"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_844-925","createTime":1719266762,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"“那个该怎么说呢？”“怎么才能用语言把这种心情表达出来呢？”“该怎么说才能把自己的想法传达给别人呢？”在不断思考这些问题并试练的过程中，人不知不觉间便掌握了语言。","range":"844-925"},{"bookId":"41922672","bookmarkId":"41922672_4_822-844","createTime":1719266755,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"没有人是不通过自身努力就可以掌握更多词语的。","range":"822-844"}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"问题4 从根本上讲，词汇量极其少","chapterUid":14,"chapterIdx":14},{"title":"作者的总结1","chapterUid":13,"chapterIdx":13},{"title":"方法3 “实况转播”眼前看到的事物","chapterUid":12,"chapterIdx":12},{"title":"前言 你拥有“把思想转化成语言”的能力吗？","chapterUid":4,"chapterIdx":4}],"book":{"bookId":"41922672","version":49566264,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/89/YueWen_41922672/s_YueWen_41922672.jpg","title":"文案达人教你5天学会表达","author":"蟇田吉昭","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KDQ]$hV:~pt2aa-.-;IUa#","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#221d00"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#251d00"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#271d00"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#363204"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#383200"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#393200"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#4e491d"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#4f4900"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#514900"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#514a00"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#696212"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#6b6200"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#676230"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#867c00"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#817b47"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#857c00"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#9b9560"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#9e9643"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#a0961f"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#a29600"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#bbb13d"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#bcb101"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#beb100"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#d0ca90"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#d3cb74"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#d9cc00"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#e8e5c2"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#f5e811"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#a0961f"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#bbb13d"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3F1E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex"